         <processinfo>
            
            <p>This collection was created as part of the reorganization of the ready reference files to consolidate non-record material pertaining to the University's human resources management functions into a reference collection. Files concerning the subject were found under various headings in Small Collections, under Employee ...; Employment Office; Human Resources, Department of; and Personnel Department, and also in artificial collections about the Personnel Department and the Human Resources Department; Policy Manuals; Wage and Salary Administration; Employee Relations Office, and Employee Unions. </p>
         
